headline: Teradyne (TER) Tapped by Amazon as Warehouse Robot Supplier
summary: Teradyne, Inc. (NASDAQ:TER) is one of the Best Industrial Automation Stocks to Buy for the Next Decade. Teradyne’s Universal Robots division has been identified as the supplier of robotic arms for Amazon’s newly unveiled warehouse robot, Vulcan, according to a report from Hunterbrook Media. This reveals Denmark-based Universal Robots as a key technology partner in […]
